<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Modern Documentation Interface</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary: #3b82f6;
            --sidebar-width: 300px;
            --header-height: 60px;
            --text-primary: #1f2937;
            --text-secondary: #6b7280;
            --bg-sidebar: #f8fafc;
            --border-color: #e5e7eb;
        }

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: var(--sidebar-width) 1fr;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        .header {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            height: var(--header-height);
            background: white;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 0 2rem;
            z-index: 100;
        }

        .search-container {
            flex: 1;
            max-width: 600px;
            position: relative;
        }

        .search-input {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
            padding-right: 3rem;
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            border-radius: 0.5rem;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }

        .search-actions {
            position: absolute;
            right: 0.5rem;
            top: 50%;
            transform: translateY(-50%);
            display: flex;
            gap: 0.5rem;
        }

        .search-actions button {
            background: none;
            border: none;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            cursor: pointer;
            padding: 0.25rem;
        }

        .sidebar {
            background: var(--bg-sidebar);
            padding: 1rem;
            padding-top: calc(var(--header-height) + 1rem);
            border-right: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            position: fixed;
            width: var(--sidebar-width);
            height: 100vh;
            overflow-y: auto;
        }

        .nav-item {
            margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
        }

        .nav-item a {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 0.5rem;
            color: var(--text-primary);
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 0.375rem;
            transition: background-color 0.2s;
        }

        .nav-item a:hover {
            background-color: #e5e7eb;
        }

        .nav-item .icon {
            width: 24px;
            height: 24px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-right: 0.75rem;
            border-radius: 0.25rem;
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            color: white;
        }

        .nav-item .count {
            margin-left: auto;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            font-size: 0.875rem;
        }

        .main-content {
            padding: 2rem;
            padding-top: calc(var(--header-height) + 2rem);
            max-width: 1200px;
        }

        .main-content h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            color: var(--text-primary);
        }

        .main-content p {
            font-size: 1.125rem;
            line-height: 1.7;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .code-editor {
            background: #1e1e1e;
            border-radius: 0.5rem;
            padding: 1rem;
            margin-top: 2rem;
            min-height: 300px;
        }

        /* Icon background colors */
        .icon-actionscript { background-color: #f43f5e; }
        .icon-angular { background-color: #dc2626; }
        .icon-classes { background-color: #8b5cf6; }
        .icon-constants { background-color: #10b981; }
        .icon-decorators { background-color: #6366f1; }
        .icon-directives { background-color: #f59e0b; }
        .icon-elements { background-color: #ec4899; }
        .icon-functions { background-color: #14b8a6; }
        .icon-arduino { background-color: #00979d; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header class="header">
        <div class="search-container">
            <input type="text" class="search-input" placeholder="Search documentation...">
            <div class="search-actions">
                <button title="Previous"><i class="fas fa-arrow-left"></i></button>
                <button title="Next"><i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <nav class="sidebar">
        <div class="nav-item">
            <a href="#actionscript">
                <span class="icon icon-actionscript">A</span>
                ActionScript
            </a>
        </div>
        <div class="nav-item">
            <a href="#angular">
                <span class="icon icon-angular">A</span>
                Angular
                <span class="count">â–¼</span>
            </a>
        </div>
        <div class="nav-item">
            <a href="#classes">
                <span class="icon icon-classes">C</span>
                Classes
                <span class="count">(157)</span>
            </a>
        </div>
        <div class="nav-item">
            <a href="#constants">
                <span class="icon icon-constants">C</span>
                Constants
                <span class="count">(242)</span>
            </a>
        </div>
        <div class="nav-item">
            <a href="#decorators">
                <span class="icon icon-decorators">D</span>
                Decorators
                <span class="count">(18)</span>
            </a>
        </div>
        <div class="nav-item">
            <a href="#directives">
                <span class="icon icon-directives">D</span>
                Directives
                <span class="count">(45)</span>
            </a>
        </div>
        <div class="nav-item">
            <a href="#elements">
                <span class="icon icon-elements">E</span>
                Elements
                <span class="count">(3)</span>
            </a>
        </div>
        <div class="nav-item">
            <a href="#arduino">
                <span class="icon icon-arduino">
                    <i class="fas fa-microchip"></i>
                </span>
                Arduino
            </a>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <main class="main-content">
        <h1>Your first Angular app</h1>
        <p>A few lines of TypeScript are all it takes to create your first Angular app. As your app grows, you can separate the markup and code into different files.</p>
        
        <h2>Try your first Angular app</h2>
        <p>The code editor contains a complete Angular app.</p>
        
        <div class="code-editor">
            <!-- Code editor content would go here -->
        </div>
    </main>
</body>
</html>